    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate adequate agreement with FDA GCBP experimental data for pressure-flow performance and hemolysis index. Model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: aleatory uncertainty in hemolysis index validation result (vr-03) arising from biological variability in blood analog samples was characterized qualitatively by engineering judgment; structured probabilistic UQ was not performed for this result.",
